## Troubleshooting

### Plugin not loading

1. Check `.claude-plugin/plugin.json` exists
2. Verify JSON syntax: `cat .claude-plugin/plugin.json | jq .`
3. Ensure commands are at plugin ROOT (not in .claude-plugin/)

### Command not found

1. Verify command file exists in `commands/` directory
2. Check YAML frontmatter has `name:` field
3. Reload Claude Code

### Hook not triggering

1. Verify event name case (PostToolUse, not postToolUse)
2. Check hooks.json syntax
3. Ensure script is executable: `chmod +x scripts/{{script}}.sh`

